                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I agree it's a difficult situation and dealing with the religious side of a person when you're not religious yourself can be akward. I'd advice that you mostly stay clear of it, since it's important to her.  Let her know what you believe about masturbation specifically and what you know. It'll be easier for her to not feel shamed if you don't, so if you feel comfortable answering personal questions about your masturbation it's probably best to do so. (Do you masturbate? How often? etc.) This should help her feel like she's ok, because she is calling you because she thinks you're ok - so it helps lift her out of the sorrow.
<br />

<br />
I wouldn't worry about if she's coming on to you or not, if she is you simply say 'No' and be done with it. I don't think it's clear whether she is or not and people sometimes do catch other people masturbating by accident! Why start an akward moment before you have to? If she becomes explicit, just say 'No' and I'm sure she'll understand. I'm confident you can explain that it's alright for her to be attracted to you, just that you're straight and that's not appealing to you - so you have to be true to yourself as well. 
<br />

<br />
If you friend is a Christian let her know that the Bible doesn't mention masturbation anywhere and the reason many churches have different views on it world wide is because it's very much a debateable topic. Her religion might be a tough conversation to have on top of the masturbation one, so I'd leave it unless she brings it up and talk about it another time. Sometimes it's best just to have a friend rather then a savior. The gay/bi debate can wait too, she's probably not ready to come out that far at this point so might as well just do it one step at a time and let her digest inbetween. I'm sure she's calling because she values your advice and I'm sure you won't disappoint as long as you express what you believe.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />1010011010 - Binary of the Beast!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
